<h1>About This Lead Intelligence Tool</h1>

<p>This application is designed to support two key personas within the recruiting and staffing industry: <strong>talent acquisition professionals</strong> and <strong>staffing service providers</strong>. Each persona is served by a dedicated page that helps them fulfill their unique workflows—either by identifying talent or by discovering hiring companies.</p>

<hr />

<h2>🔹 Lead Collection Tool</h2>
<p><strong>Audience:</strong> Technical recruiters filling urgent or hard-to-hire roles, such as AI Engineers.</p>
<p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Identify and extract individual leads—complete with contact details—from platforms like LinkedIn, GitHub, and TikTok.</p>
<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>
<ul>
    <li>Search by keyword and platform (e.g., "AI Engineer" on LinkedIn)</li>
    <li>Email domain and phone number filtering</li>
    <li>Paginated results and CSV export</li>
</ul>

<hr />

<h2>🔹 Talent Demand Page</h2>
<p><strong>Audience:</strong> Staffing service providers, business development professionals, and contractor agencies.</p>
<p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Surface companies that are actively hiring for targeted roles using the SerpApi Google Jobs API.</p>
<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>
<ul>
    <li>Search by job title and location</li>
    <li>Grouped listings by company with job details</li>
    <li>Optional job description viewing and CSV export</li>
</ul>

<hr />

<h2>🔁 How the Pages Work Together</h2>
<p>The two pages form a full-cycle lead funnel:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Talent Demand Page</strong>: Discover who’s hiring</li>
    <li><strong>Lead Collection Page</strong>: Find and contact talent to fulfill those openings</li>
</ul>

<p>Whether you're prospecting for new clients or filling roles with verified leads, this tool helps unify both sides of the staffing equation.</p>

<p><em>Built with recruiters in mind. Powered by SerpApi. Designed for results.</em></p>
